{"data":{"strapiHomeVideo":{"video":{"localFile":{"publicURL":"/static/296855185e7c4213df7a99c9052cdbb7/We_Chat202311_13357a81c2.mp4"}}},"allStrapiCorporateNew":{"nodes":[{"desc":"江苏沪申钛白科技有限公司是由上海江沪实业有限公司、上海江沪钛白化工制品有限公司，上海凌升精制钛白粉有限公司一起合并重新在江苏南通投资兴办的，其下还包括江苏沪申药业有限公司，是食品添加剂二氧化钛国家标准主起草单位，拥有多品种二氧化钛研发生产能力，强大的检测分析能力，拥有国家CNAS认证的实验室。公司熟悉二氧化钛国内外产品特性和行业发展现状与进展，愿与行业内各方朋友助力行业健康发展，推动健康中国进一步落地。\n【供应类型】食品配料&添加剂\n【产品/服务】主营产品：\n食品添加剂二氧化钛、钛白粉、白色素、氢氧化钙、食品增白剂、复配着色乳化剂、高分散白色素。","id":"54adbdcc-3c1b-56e9-a825-83c948b4569e","time":"2023-09-20","title":"江苏沪申钛白科技有限公司相关证件","media":[{"localFile":{"publicURL":"/static/719babebd266361a3b10d6901d2b9787/20231104000944_f5b37728cd.jpg","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#3888c8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/719babebd266361a3b10d6901d2b9787/83eab/20231104000944_f5b37728cd.jpg","srcSet":"/static/719babebd266361a3b10d6901d2b9787/5b128/20231104000944_f5b37728cd.jpg 2091w,\n/static/719babebd266361a3b10d6901d2b9787/81095/20231104000944_f5b37728cd.jpg 4182w,\n/static/719babebd266361a3b10d6901d2b9787/83eab/20231104000944_f5b37728cd.jpg 8364w","sizes":"(min-width: 8364px) 8364px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/719babebd266361a3b10d6901d2b9787/35542/20231104000944_f5b37728cd.webp 2091w,\n/static/719babebd266361a3b10d6901d2b9787/7ee28/20231104000944_f5b37728cd.webp 4182w,\n/static/719babebd266361a3b10d6901d2b9787/f0f6d/20231104000944_f5b37728cd.webp 8364w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 8364px) 8364px, 100vw"}]},"width":8364,"height":2578}}}}]},{"desc":"金红石型钛白粉广泛应用于涂料、塑料、橡胶、油墨等行业。金红石型钛白可以达到和二氧化钛一样的技术性能，大大降低原材料成本。市面上有很多假的金红石型钛白粉，会导致塑料加工中析出白色物质，里面混了很多钙粉。为了调节添加钙粉引起的吸油量变化，里面添加了蜡粉，让很多消费者上当受骗。那么如何鉴别金红石型钛白粉的真伪呢?","id":"4a56ea5f-0b74-5377-9b9e-c0534ff989b3","time":"2023-03-17","title":"金红石型钛白粉","media":[{"localFile":{"publicURL":"/static/ec4e3f31f7f6319088ff1a124a005b6e/f5220f39_1017_4e06_8aad_1145dda2a47d_jpg_1920xaf_acce6831ee.jpg","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#88c8e8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/ec4e3f31f7f6319088ff1a124a005b6e/33355/f5220f39_1017_4e06_8aad_1145dda2a47d_jpg_1920xaf_acce6831ee.jpg","srcSet":"/static/ec4e3f31f7f6319088ff1a124a005b6e/6efd2/f5220f39_1017_4e06_8aad_1145dda2a47d_jpg_1920xaf_acce6831ee.jpg 480w,\n/static/ec4e3f31f7f6319088ff1a124a005b6e/23a9e/f5220f39_1017_4e06_8aad_1145dda2a47d_jpg_1920xaf_acce6831ee.jpg 960w,\n/static/ec4e3f31f7f6319088ff1a124a005b6e/33355/f5220f39_1017_4e06_8aad_1145dda2a47d_jpg_1920xaf_acce6831ee.jpg 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/ec4e3f31f7f6319088ff1a124a005b6e/ad76d/f5220f39_1017_4e06_8aad_1145dda2a47d_jpg_1920xaf_acce6831ee.webp 480w,\n/static/ec4e3f31f7f6319088ff1a124a005b6e/1ca0d/f5220f39_1017_4e06_8aad_1145dda2a47d_jpg_1920xaf_acce6831ee.webp 960w,\n/static/ec4e3f31f7f6319088ff1a124a005b6e/707e4/f5220f39_1017_4e06_8aad_1145dda2a47d_jpg_1920xaf_acce6831ee.webp 1920w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}]},"width":1920,"height":600}}}}]},{"desc":"中国国际食品添加剂和配料展览会FIC\n江苏沪申钛白科技有限公司（原）上海江沪钛白化工制品有限公司\n本公司创始人谢益元先生1983年在湖南邵阳创办了湖南江沪实业有限公司，1990年迁移到上海;1992年正式成立上海江沪实业有限公司;因工厂的需要，投资了上海江沪钛白制品有限公司，接着研发的化学纤维用二氧化钛取得成功。2000年又相继研发了食品级二氧化钛和药品级二氧化钛，结束了该领域二氧化钛只能依靠进口的历史。\n\n2016年6月在江苏省通州湾江海联动开发示范区长江路210号购买土地近80亩，自建了51660m的6栋厂房和综合楼。并于2016年10月13日注册成立了江苏沪申钛白科技有限公司，注册资金10,000万元，核准生产和销售精细二氧化钛系列产品。公司继承了原上海公司已有的生产技术，为使二氧化钛精加工更加科学、合理，不断添置生产设备和检测仪器，现生产规模在原上海公司的基础上有大幅度提升，建有万级(C级)微生物检测及CNAS实验中心，已于2022年9月评审顺利通过。公司还组建了产品研发团队，确保不断有研发的新产品供应市场。","id":"406c3852-47af-55ec-bd10-a615252df983","time":"2023-03-17","title":"中国国际食品添加剂和配料展览会FIC","media":[{"localFile":{"publicURL":"/static/933391e35a799ec001ddd58d9746d91a/20230714012343_effa9a8a68.png","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/933391e35a799ec001ddd58d9746d91a/cb649/20230714012343_effa9a8a68.png","srcSet":"/static/933391e35a799ec001ddd58d9746d91a/9f819/20230714012343_effa9a8a68.png 480w,\n/static/933391e35a799ec001ddd58d9746d91a/f6bf2/20230714012343_effa9a8a68.png 960w,\n/static/933391e35a799ec001ddd58d9746d91a/cb649/20230714012343_effa9a8a68.png 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/933391e35a799ec001ddd58d9746d91a/44814/20230714012343_effa9a8a68.webp 480w,\n/static/933391e35a799ec001ddd58d9746d91a/88ae8/20230714012343_effa9a8a68.webp 960w,\n/static/933391e35a799ec001ddd58d9746d91a/b9364/20230714012343_effa9a8a68.webp 1920w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}]},"width":1920,"height":466}}}}]}]},"strapiHotProduct":{"products":[{"title":"二氧化钛、白色素 ","id":"6e020924-11cc-57a8-8c0c-d232c9426657","image":{"localFile":{"publicURL":"/static/81d7343ec52e26649482b9a8b5c38055/002_a93f6a0f60.jpg","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#b8b8b8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/81d7343ec52e26649482b9a8b5c38055/9366f/002_a93f6a0f60.jpg","srcSet":"/static/81d7343ec52e26649482b9a8b5c38055/f7b1a/002_a93f6a0f60.jpg 175w,\n/static/81d7343ec52e26649482b9a8b5c38055/7ba70/002_a93f6a0f60.jpg 350w,\n/static/81d7343ec52e26649482b9a8b5c38055/9366f/002_a93f6a0f60.jpg 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/81d7343ec52e26649482b9a8b5c38055/51bad/002_a93f6a0f60.webp 175w,\n/static/81d7343ec52e26649482b9a8b5c38055/6cac9/002_a93f6a0f60.webp 350w,\n/static/81d7343ec52e26649482b9a8b5c38055/ec00d/002_a93f6a0f60.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":700}}}}},{"title":"复配着色剂食品添加剂","id":"75dc5bd5-f4a2-52d4-ab98-5205717a24bb","image":{"localFile":{"publicURL":"/static/e0ed36b9f912de52a3ee9cc372b244a7/u_2467613268_3960487205_and_fm_199_and_app_68_and_f_JPEG_5220650067.jpg","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#c8c8c8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/e0ed36b9f912de52a3ee9cc372b244a7/0f5ce/u_2467613268_39604872